code: public Tuple11Builder<T0, T1, T2, T3, T4, T5, T6, T7, T8, T9, T10> add(T0 value0, T1 value1, T2 value2, T3 value3, T4 value4, T5 value5, T6 value6, T7 value7, T8 value8, T9 value9, T10 value10) {     tuples.add(new Tuple11<>(value0, value1, value2, value3, value4, value5, value6, value7, value8, value9, value10)).     return this. }
